{
  "texts": [
    "• We use code generation to produce fine-tuned versions of the prompt for specific platforms.",
    "We provide an example for a text-to-text, and two text-to-image generative AI systems: OpenAI, and Midjourney and Stable Diffusion, respectively.",
    "• We generate code that queries generative AI systems using platform-specific prompts and captures their responses.",
    "In particular, we provide implementations to prompt OpenAI's GPT models (for text-to-text generation) and Stable Diffusion (for text-to-image generation).",
    "• We synthesize validation checks that, using the information included in the DSL and without requiring any user intervention, queries another generative AI system to validate that the responses fulfill the user's requirements using the LLM-as-a-judge paradigm [16]."
  ]
}